00:15:47,120 --> 00:15:50,800
Dirige l'orchestra
il maestro Valeriano Chiaravalle.

220
00:15:50,840 --> 00:15:54,040
[APPLAUSI]

221
00:15:54,080 --> 00:15:58,960
Con il codice 02,
Eddie Brock con Fabrizio Moro!

222
00:15:59,000 --> 00:16:02,520
